name: Qlucore Data File
summary: Learn about .GEDATA files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: The data stored in a GEDATA file can be visualized and statistically analyzed in the Qlucore Omics Explorer software.

description: Data file used by Qlucore Omics Explorer, a bioinformatics data analysis and visualization program; contains a complete data frame, including sample and variable annotations; saved in a tab-delimited text format.
